{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1969,"month":1,"day":19}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席革命路线奏凯歌","authors":["汽车驾驶员赵景玉〖HH/换行〗DW：四六九九部队"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们开动那“解放牌”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大地都跑遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红彤彤的天呵红彤彤的地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限风光呵激动着心田！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过风雪高原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到关卡哨所，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士为毛主席革命路线站岗、放哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰天雪地也浑身暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰过座座工厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过广阔田间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓革命促生产的热浪冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命凯歌四处传遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过奔腾长江水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过千里黄河岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民愤怒批判大叛徒刘少奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志昂扬卷巨澜！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过万重关山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过塞外江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知识青年奔向农村落户、扎根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在广阔天地里把红心锤炼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的最新指示象春雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浇得花红叶绿果满园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文化大革命洪流滚滚向前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的河山今朝更好看。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}